{"tid":1515992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日係咪做錯咗一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:38:12.000Z","uid":154406,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ff12cbeda5628ac07ca11e738d350cbe0b1a81","tid":1515992,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日求其行咗入一間salon洗剪吹，咁好快佢安排我洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個洗頭妹幾靚，又着熱褲show長腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我就瞓低俾佢幫我洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢手勢幾好，又會按摩埋頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺我好enjoy嘅時候，佢問咗我一句：先生你有冇邊度痕啊？之後我答佢：下面好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢即刻成個人變晒咁，又用熱水幫我洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又好大力咁拉我啲頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知得罪佢啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁嘅服務態度真心唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會再幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求巴打教路我做錯啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身仲諗住同佢傾吓計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638b3832d34b2c4c9b8823ed100156aa73fb344b","tid":1515992,"uid":173695,"like":0,"dislik